Package: OPSR
Title: Ordinal Probit Switching Regression
Version: 0.0.0.9009
Authors@R: c(person("Daniel", "Heimgartner", email = "d.heimgartners@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0643-8690")),
    person("Xinyi", "Wang", email = "xinyi174@mit.edu", role = c("aut"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3564-9147")))
Description: Estimates ordinal probit switching regression models - a Heckman
    type selection model with an ordinal selection and continuous outcomes.
    Different model specifications are allowed for each treatment/regime.
